Name: Monkey Hit
About the game: In this funny 2D platformer you play the role of a brave monkey, whose path leads through many levels, armed only with a staff and throwing stones. Go through long levels filled with various enemies and dangers. Jump, run, throw stones and hit enemies with a pole. Collect coins along the way. A game for the whole family.
